      "Edit this file only -- never edit the script for data changes",
      "Each group is processed independently and rendered as a separate section",
      "groups.threat_intel.feeds -- security research, advisories, exploits, vendor blogs",
      "groups.news.feeds -- trusted news sources; filter by country_tag in future",
      "groups.government.feeds -- official government cyber and national security publications",
      "fetch_cache_ttl_seconds -- how long to cache a raw feed response locally before re-fetching",
      "Run: python prism.py --check-feeds to verify all feed URLs",
      "Run: python prism.py --set-key otx to store AlienVault OTX API key",
      "Feed URL audit 2026-03-29: Fixed MSRC, WithSecure, CyberWire, Secureworks->Sophos, Picus dedup, Europol; removed dead Reuters; disabled ENISA (RSS discontinued); noted CISA RSS status",
